title: NHS National Honor Society inducts 40 new members (Newark City School District)
text: ( Source : Newark City School District ) Newark High School 's National Honor Society inducted 40 new members recently. These 40 students are leaders in the school, working hard both in and outside the classroom. Click here to find a photo
